2000-09-19  Sascha Schumann  <sascha@schumann.cx>

    * ext/standard/url_scanner_ex.c
      ext/standard/url_scanner_ex.re:
    Another speedup by avoiding string copies.

    15% speed gain in test case (rewriting 1M URLs).

