1999-10-19  Thies C. Arntzen  <thies@digicol.de>

    * NEWS: added === operator support (type *and* value match) . samples:
    (1 == "1") is true
    (1 === "1") is false (integer != string)
    (0 == false) is true
    (0 === false) is false (integer != boolean)

